{"tid":2036270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】美帝來了！！！","createTime":"2020-05-26T11:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T12:01:16.000Z","uid":231886,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8e088d1bbbae80b610520c439d276e4da08600cc","tid":2036270,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">美帝來了！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n#美國探子回報<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">美國發來的消息<br />\n指華府將對北京發強烈警告<br />\n最快星期四出手<br />\n宣布第一波制裁中共行動<br />\n針對參與國安法官員<br />\n若中共不剎停<br />\n將再下一城<br />\n包括可能在美國大選前<br />\n開始分階段取消香港獨立關稅區地位</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#內地探子回報 #自行判斷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n內地情報則指<br />\n習近平對香港國安法推展<br />\n「信心滿滿」<br />\n即使遇黨內反對聲音<br />\n但習堅持必須訂立國安條例<br />\n沒有讓步空間亦做好一切準備<br />\n包括提供財政補償及一切支持<br />\n予被美國制裁的官員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n轉自：<a href=\"https://t.me/easternhawkeye/19239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasternhawkeye%2F19239&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=d08ee7cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/easternhawkeye/19239</a>"},{"pid":"5cd69f4327792c625aed96dffdc24599aa57aa80","tid":2036270,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b07de9727ec0bbe2feb75dd66641bfe900ad39c3","tid":2036270,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0047d760acb1d1aa0ede19678f76a402785fd64","tid":2036270,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9526119d434774176bf7532d3a1d0e9c726a657","tid":2036270,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike"